These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, turquise, mauve
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, drama, mystery, musical
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person watching spy movies is between the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Color      | turquise        | mauve     | fuchsia | light-blue      |
| Movie-Genre          | mystery | drama    | spy      | musical  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

