 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of techno##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the tower house##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the palace house is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
12. the farmhouse house is between the person driving the roller and the cape-cod house##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of soul##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
